  "content_html": "<h1 id=\"legacy-title-sort-fix\">Legacy Title Sort Fix</h1>\n\n<p>Script:</p>\n\n<div class=\"language-bash highlighter-rouge\"><div class=\"highlight\"><pre class=\"highlight\"><code>./scripts/fix_missing_title_sort.py\n</code></pre></div></div>\n\n<p>Generated site JSON no longer persists <code class=\"language-plaintext highlighter-rouge\">title_sort</code>.\nThis helper remains only for older or hand-authored <code class=\"language-plaintext highlighter-rouge\">_works</code> front matter that still uses that field.</p>\n\n<p>Dry-run:</p>\n\n<div class=\"language-bash highlighter-rouge\"><div class=\"highlight\"><pre class=\"highlight\"><code>./scripts/fix_missing_title_sort.py\n</code></pre></div></div>\n\n<p>Write changes:</p>\n\n<div class=\"language-bash highlighter-rouge\"><div class=\"highlight\"><pre class=\"highlight\"><code>./scripts/fix_missing_title_sort.py <span class=\"nt\">--write</span>\n</code></pre></div></div>\n\n<p>Scope to selected IDs or ranges:</p>\n\n<div class=\"language-bash highlighter-rouge\"><div class=\"highlight\"><pre class=\"highlight\"><code>./scripts/fix_missing_title_sort.py <span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n  <span class=\"nt\">--work-ids</span> 66-74,38,40 <span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n  <span class=\"nt\">--write</span>\n</code></pre></div></div>\n\n<h2 id=\"related-references\">Related References</h2>\n\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/docs/?scope=studio&doc=scripts-overview\">Scripts Overview</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/docs/?scope=studio&doc=scripts-generate-work-pages\">Generate Work Pages</a></li>\n</ul>\n",
